title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description:
Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the report containing a table with highlight/map functionality.
2. Attempt to export the data from the table using the export feature.

OB: 
- N/A

EB: 
Export the data in the table successfully without any exceptions.

SR: 
1. Open the report containing a table with highlight/map functionality.
2. Select the export option from the menu or toolbar.
3. Choose the desired data export format.
4. Verify that the data is exported successfully without any exceptions being thrown.
